{
  "id": "RAW_523f05",
  "title": "用 DeepSeek 徒手造一个能对话的 AI 简历，助你当场拿下 Offer。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647671604&idx=1&sn=ee74a151aa5ff7836e1da7562a1222df",
  "date": "2025-06-03 01:03:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">故事是这样的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我最近一直在招人，想招点人帮我分担一些压力，全职的实习的啥的都可以。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我这再怎么说，也是一个跟AI有关的地方，所以很多人在投简历的时候，都会写很多跟AI相关的经历，我甚至收到过很多AI生成的简历。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多写的很玄乎，什么掌握全链路工作流，独立搭建xx系统，深度参与xx项目，掌握xx行业资源等等，但是一面，问用过最惊艳的AI产品是啥，10个有9个说的是DeepSeek，再问最常用的AI产品是啥，还是DeepSeek。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再追问还用过哪些其他的AI产品？10个有9个说的就是豆包。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;DmkAdFTcgo3FysxBioAczzLRnBb&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;基本上很容易看出来，小词儿一套一套的，什么掌握全链路工作流，独立搭建xx系统，深度参与xx项目，掌握xx行业资源，看着就特别像AI生成的，一问，果然是。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+24&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7506039434499129346&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;933807b9-57fb-4c7d-bb90-fa090e0f2adf&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:3,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:14,&quot;end&quot;:90},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;LjTsdi50LofxuNxxBnxcdZ1xnRf&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，我觉得我现在对DeepSeek有点PTSD可能就是从这来的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过，这个端午节，我收到了一个让我觉得有点与众不同、眼前一亮的简历。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/772b5c8a-edcf-4b0f-8fca-c8d11f408900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3212962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187919\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/772b5c8a-edcf-4b0f-8fca-c8d11f408900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一次，看到一个人，把自己变成了AI简历。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我点进去看了下。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500187914\" data-ratio=\"0.649074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5837d6e4-49ae-4a5e-559a-38306681eb00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5837d6e4-49ae-4a5e-559a-38306681eb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然已经跟她沟通过，写出来没啥问题，但是为了保护隐私，我还是都打码了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然整体设计的很青涩，非常的AI，但是我依然觉得，这个非常的有意思。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟，在千篇一律的PDF简历之后，我终于看到了一个，不一样的。是用AI编程把自己的简历，给可视化的东西。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fe247c99-6783-4833-69c6-d3c1d8507900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8101851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187915\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fe247c99-6783-4833-69c6-d3c1d8507900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是如果只是这样，我觉得也还好，毕竟PDF做成可视化网页已经流行很久很久了，这也不算啥很特别的事，但是最让我觉得有意思的是，她还在里面，塞了一个AI对话。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5940837f-e854-4a3b-f074-5a3c61863800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8648148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187916\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5940837f-e854-4a3b-f074-5a3c61863800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以在这个网页里面，直接跟她的分身对话，来询问她过去的经历。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个就很酷很有趣了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">测了一下，大概率就是把她自己的简历和过去的一些作品集放在了里面做了个知识库，并没有针对AI助手去写一些特别的Prompt或者是一些特定的数据集，来针对性的给面试官一些简历上没有的答案。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给出来的答案，也基本都是PDF简历上，已经有的东西。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是在我看来，这事根本无所谓。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">因为这个形式所传达出来的态度和意义，远远超出与真正问答的内容本身，我也相信不会有任何一个面试官，会真的用这种AI简历给出的回答来做参考，来定生死。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但当你看遍了PDF简历之后，看到个东西，我相信你绝对不会怀疑，这个人到底是否对AI感兴趣，这个人到底会不会用AI。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开什么玩笑，这要是都不会用的话，那谁算会啊？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">于是我第二天直接约了面试，聊了40分钟以后，询问了很多技术细节，虽然中间有磕磕绊绊，但是整体我依然非常满意，面试完的当天晚上，我就发了Offer，来担任我这边的运营实习生岗位。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cde6bb14-0fee-48c9-e6a3-cacf94738a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23481781376518218\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"494\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"494\" data-backh=\"116\" data-imgfileid=\"500187918\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cde6bb14-0fee-48c9-e6a3-cacf94738a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">江山代有才人出，我自然，也希望，能招到越来越多的这样的朋友。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看到这，我相信很多朋友可能会问，这个AI简历，到底咋做啊？特别是把AI对话嵌入到网页里面，我不懂代码，做不来啊。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">坦率的讲，把PDF简历生成可视化网页，这事特别简单，但是如果你想在网页里面，插入一个AI对话窗口，这确实还是麻烦了一点，因为要用API来去搭，对于没有代码背景的朋友，还是有一些复杂的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是我想了一个有手就行的方案，就是用Dify+Gemini或者Dify+DeepSeek+YouWare的方式，来徒手搭一个。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">原理其实很简单，CatBot这种形式肯定我们就不从头写了，那太麻烦了，一般就用一个智能体平台搭完，然后发布并嵌入到网页上。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里我自己首选Dify。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：https://cloud.dify.ai/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ddff5bd5-b262-49db-b137-9590a4550200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6008563273073264\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2102\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187920\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ddff5bd5-b262-49db-b137-9590a4550200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我这里，用一个马斯克求职来举个例子（纯整活，无任何主观恶意）。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我让OpenAI DeepResearch给我输出了一份，马斯克的简历。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/54435fea-845a-44b4-261b-ef13a5b47700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4986072423398329\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1077\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187921\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/54435fea-845a-44b4-261b-ef13a5b47700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，简历的PDF是这样的，相比大家很多人的简历，要朴素好多。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/86a8c67e-d57e-44d0-6d8d-19610a811200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.289855072463768\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187922\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/86a8c67e-d57e-44d0-6d8d-19610a811200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在做个人网站之前，我们先去Dify上，搭一个可根据特定知识库问答的ChatBot。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">进来以后，创建一个空白应用。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c8bab1f0-687d-4d5b-b6b6-eef9ed1dca00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187923\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c8bab1f0-687d-4d5b-b6b6-eef9ed1dca00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一进来以后，是一个看着好像很复杂的工作流界面，但是不要慌，信我，其实很简单。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8fee925-2034-4e23-4daf-7951e9c78e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187924\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8fee925-2034-4e23-4daf-7951e9c78e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先，在开始和LLM节点之间，插入一个知识检索，这玩意就是知识库。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3fcd0552-2d23-4889-3da8-20bf6c2a5d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6990740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187925\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3fcd0552-2d23-4889-3da8-20bf6c2a5d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，进入到顶部的知识库页面，创建一个知识库。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/25ba615c-4310-42d2-0a70-340713368d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24259259259259258\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187926\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/25ba615c-4310-42d2-0a70-340713368d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">正常上传你想要的单个文件，比如我就传了个马斯克的简历PDF上去。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在索引方式下，选择经济就行，主要就是咱们简历其实也没几个字，没多少信息，效果也没有差太多，还能省一堆很多人看不懂的关于Embedding模型的事，还免费。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9871eae4-4446-46ec-a85f-3e9b63350700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47605500237079185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2109\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187929\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9871eae4-4446-46ec-a85f-3e9b63350700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后点保存并处理就行，几秒钟后，知识库就弄好了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/39d12b48-d96e-4f98-7247-6054104b2e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5068394528437725\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1389\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187930\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/39d12b48-d96e-4f98-7247-6054104b2e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点前往文档，就能进入知识库详情，我觉得一个简历PDF好像没啥意思，于是又补了一本《马斯克传》进去。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PS：Dify最大支持15M的PDF，如果PDF大小超出的话，可以直接用WPS进行PDF瘦身。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/270fabc6-9735-4af1-00f5-7e9c7ac5a700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25855263157894737\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1520\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187931\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/270fabc6-9735-4af1-00f5-7e9c7ac5a700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">十几秒后，我们的知识库就弄好了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">回到工作室Tab（我也不知道它为啥叫工作室），在这个知识检索节点中，添加刚刚弄好的知识库。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/19d7ffbd-b2df-4ba6-f7dd-1a80e89d2b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.537962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187932\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/19d7ffbd-b2df-4ba6-f7dd-1a80e89d2b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，在LLM模块中，在上下文部分，选择第一个知识检索。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f84d7691-f756-4066-d452-637d19371300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5203703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187933\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f84d7691-f756-4066-d452-637d19371300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再在下面的Prompt部分，点击函数，插入上下文。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/68e21a9a-737d-4482-1cc5-8036a24e4400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5509259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187935\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/68e21a9a-737d-4482-1cc5-8036a24e4400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里的上下文，其实就是会抓取到的你文档里的知识。有一个小小的规范，就是我非常建议在上下文的上下，写一个XML标签，把它包裹起来，效果会好一些。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我瞎写的Prompt是这样的：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"xml\"><code><span leaf=\"\">我是马斯克，我正在求职。</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\">我最近破产了，xAI、特斯拉、星舰都倒闭了，我想找一份工作，理想工作是中国公务员，实在不行滴滴司机或者送外卖也行。</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\">我现在正在跟面试官面试，请你根据接受到的问题和我给出的信息：</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__tag\">&lt;</span><span class=\"code-snippet__tag\"><span class=\"code-snippet__name\">context</span></span><span class=\"code-snippet__tag\">&gt;</span></span></code><code><span leaf=\"\">上下文</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__tag\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"code-snippet__tag\"><span class=\"code-snippet__name\">context</span></span><span class=\"code-snippet__tag\">&gt;</span></span></code><code><span leaf=\"\">从一个求职者的角度，进行回答。</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">流程编排，这就弄好了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，最后，最关键的一步，就是具体要回答的大模型的选择。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里，我自己是用的硅基流动上的DeepSeek V3。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/71fa00ae-631a-42e2-9335-5cb9e8d55d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6073926073926074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1001\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187938\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/71fa00ae-631a-42e2-9335-5cb9e8d55d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eda343b9-aaad-41ca-6de3-617fb6969400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.57125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"800\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187937\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eda343b9-aaad-41ca-6de3-617fb6969400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，你们要是用火山方舟、通义、智谱啥的都没问题，自己配置就好，这里我就不过多赘述了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一切完成之后，我们点击发布。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">至于怎么把它嵌入你的网站，特别简单，当你点击发布之后，你会发现，下面有一个嵌入网站的功能。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/566081a3-912e-43a5-0313-b4f0c40dc600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7775280898876404\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"445\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"445\" data-backh=\"346\" data-imgfileid=\"500187939\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/566081a3-912e-43a5-0313-b4f0c40dc600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点开它，你会发现有三种ChatBot样式，三种代码。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbda9f05-8cef-40ae-d816-5b05a4e22200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6946107784431138\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"668\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187941\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbda9f05-8cef-40ae-d816-5b05a4e22200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你不需要知道这些代码是干啥的，选择一个你心仪的样式，复制下来就行。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，打开你的Gemini或者DeepSeek或者Claude，把你的简历文件+可视化网页Prompt+这段代码，一起发送过去。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你要是用Gemini的话，记得把下面的那个Canvas打开。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/035c9cbd-2c78-407f-8279-5b8b6fd79c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4157740993184031\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1027\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187943\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/035c9cbd-2c78-407f-8279-5b8b6fd79c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b47f7e3f-340a-415a-73c3-e403cd0b4600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6715976331360947\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1014\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187942\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b47f7e3f-340a-415a-73c3-e403cd0b4600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很快啊，两个好哥们，一顿给你写，写了几分钟以后，就写完了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4d8fb935-5922-4512-7fde-48ab1f12b000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44537037037037036\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187944\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4d8fb935-5922-4512-7fde-48ab1f12b000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果是Gemini，你就可以直接，把网址分享给你的朋友或者直接发出去了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2c40d206-e843-4273-c4bd-6abd04244600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25027932960893856\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"895\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187945\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2c40d206-e843-4273-c4bd-6abd04244600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对方是可以打开的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你是DeepSeek，可以看到，这里有下载和运行按钮。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57b2e535-d203-43ab-4128-7f32eec1cb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5257633587786259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1048\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187946\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/57b2e535-d203-43ab-4128-7f32eec1cb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">运行的话可以直接看预览，但是，没法把链接分享给朋友看。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47afc5df-835c-4c62-1e1e-103a90860300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4388888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187947\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47afc5df-835c-4c62-1e1e-103a90860300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">（别问我为啥DeepSeek给马斯克匹配了一个蜘蛛侠，我也一脸懵逼，咋，因为蜘蛛侠是钢铁侠的接班人吗。。。）</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你也可以接着跟DeepSeek对话，或者直接把这个Html文档下载下来，然后，打开我们的老朋友，YouWare（不是错别字，之前他们叫YourWare，现在改名叫YouWare了）</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：https://www.youware.com/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/56639b97-303f-498f-7b10-6a5eab9c1300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5083333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187949\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/56639b97-303f-498f-7b10-6a5eab9c1300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把我们刚刚在DeepSeek上下载的Html文件，直接扔上去。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，你就会获得一个链接，就能看到马斯克的AI简历了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c0ea9223-0a89-48a9-5317-058711cc7a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7555555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187950\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c0ea9223-0a89-48a9-5317-058711cc7a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最右边那个AI对话，是真的可以对话的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f1de4229-309c-4a58-f708-6bd04e699600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7240740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187951\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f1de4229-309c-4a58-f708-6bd04e699600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，因为是封装的SDK，所以虽然简单傻瓜，但是样式确实不是很好改，这是一个弊端。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以这块如果你有非常个性化的、自定义的对话样式需求，那我建议，还是用API开发吧。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，我想说。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">AI，让我们的简历有了更多被看见的可能性，也许会让大家的找工作之路变得更加顺利。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过说到底，我写这篇的目的，不是为了让大家玩儿命地去卷简历。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而是让大家看到一种，用AI把自己变得更好的可能性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI简历很酷炫，但不是最重要的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真正重要和有价值的，是探索未知领域的好奇心，持续学习的努力，即使一时半会儿没有得到想要的结果也不去摆烂的韧劲儿，以及在roll一遍又一遍的过程中逐渐成长起来的你自己。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;DmkAdFTcgo3FysxBioAczzLRnBb&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;真正重要和有价值的，是探索未知领域的好奇心，持续学习的努力，即使一时半会儿没有得到想要的结果也不去摆烂的韧劲儿，以及在roll一遍又一遍的过程中逐渐成长起来的你自己。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+2b&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7506039434499129346&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;f4bc5f33-29df-4d5f-93a9-fe7ac86719af&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:101,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:83},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;DbejdnVl8oxkG5xYIzYcofMOnte&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当面试官看到你的简历时，他们也同样能够透过简历看到这些，看到背后的那个你。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">祝大家在这个不那么好的大环境里，顺利找到自己满意的工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然有了工作就会发现，工作中有的是比简历难搞的东西。不过这些都是人生这个开放世界游戏中，很有意思的剧情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">愿你借助AI的力量，成长，进化，一步步走向属于自己的顶峰。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克、水杉</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章提供了一个使用 Dify 和大型语言模型构建交互式 AI 简历的实操指南。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章提供了一个使用 Dify 和大型语言模型构建交互式 AI 简历的实操指南。",
  "summary": "作者分享了其作为招聘者收到一份包含 AI 对话功能简历的经历，认为这种新颖形式能有效帮助求职者在众多 PDF 简历中脱颖而出，展示其 AI 应用能力。文章核心是一份详细的教程，指导读者如何使用 Dify 平台搭建基于个人简历知识库的 ChatBot 后端，并结合大型语言模型（如 DeepSeek 或 Gemini）生成包含该 ChatBot 嵌入代码的网页前端，最后通过 YouWare 等工具进行发布。强调了这种 AI 简历形式传递出的积极态度和创新精神，认为其价值远超对话内容本身，是求职者运用 AI 提升自我的一个具体实践案例。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "交互式 AI 简历能帮助求职者有效突出个人能力和对 AI 的掌握度",
      "explanation": "通过构建一个可对话的个人简历，求职者能以创新方式展示其技术实践能力和积极探索态度，在传统简历形式中形成差异化优势。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用 Dify 等平台可无需代码快速搭建基于知识库的 AI 对话后端",
      "explanation": "文章详细介绍了 Dify 的知识检索节点和工作流配置，简化了将简历内容转化为可供模型问答知识库的过程，降低了技术门槛。"
    },
    {
      "point": "结合大模型生成前端代码实现 AI 对话嵌入网页",
      "explanation": "演示了如何利用 Gemini 或 DeepSeek 等 AI 模型生成包含 Dify 嵌入代码的 HTML 页面，并借助 YouWare 等工具发布，使得非开发者也能实现可视化 AI 简历。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "第一次，看到一个人，把自己变成了 AI 简历。",
    "但当你看遍了 PDF 简历之后，看到个东西，我相信你绝对不会怀疑，这个人到底是否对 AI 感兴趣，这个人到底会不会用 AI。",
    "因为这个形式所传达出来的态度和意义，远远超出与真正问答的内容本身...",
    "我想了一个有手就行的方案，就是用 Dify+Gemini 或者 Dify+DeepSeek+YouWare 的方式，来徒手搭一个。",
    "AI，让我们的简历有了更多被看见的可能性，也许会让大家的找工作之路变得更加顺利。"
  ],
